metadata.name: The wormhole
metadata.description:
wormhole, a solution of the field equations in German-born physicist Albert Einstein's theory of general relativity, resembles a tunnel between two black holes or other points in space-time. Such a tunnel would provide a shortcut between its endpoints.

The artwork has been created in Zbrush for modeling the character and blender for the environment and lighting and after effect to add more details and enhance the colors and premier pro for final editing and sound

Resolution : 1080 by 1080
30 FBS
